《冤親債主》定於2017年上1月13日在美國上映<ref>{{cite news |url=http://deadline.com/2016/04/bye-bye-man-release-date-moved-again-by-stx-1201741776/ |title=‘Bye Bye Man’ Release Date Shifted Again By STX Entertainment |work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline]] |date=2016-04-21 |accessdate=2017-01-05 |archive-date=2019-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191111172524/https://deadline.com/2016/04/bye-bye-man-release-date-moved-again-by-stx-1201741776/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。電影的美國映期原本定於2016年10月14日，後延遲至2016年6月3日<ref>{{cite news |url=http://variety.com/2016/film/news/carrie-anne-moss-bye-bye-man-june-1201728444/ |title=STX Thriller ‘Bye Bye Man’ Moved Up for June Release |work=Variety |date=2016-03-11 |accessdate=2017-01-05 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108155313/https://variety.com/2016/film/news/carrie-anne-moss-bye-bye-man-june-1201728444/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，之後也曾改至2016年12月9日。

